title: Most Addictive Records - #NEWBORN
description: Most Addictive Records proudly present to you their first album, #NEWBORN Featuring tracks from Dubsidia, The Brig, Kick The Habit, Flatmate, Axel Boy and stacks more, the album covers everything from dubstep and trap to glitch hop and more experimental electronica. There are exclusive tracks from Dubsidia, Flatmate, Trendkiller and The Brig only available as part of this album. This is just the beginning for what is going to be a very exciting journey for Most Addictive Records.
